just say of it it is possible and if its yes and you know how say that to plz

ragean[/quote]

Okay you can change your network IP if your on a router [192.168.2.*]

You can change your external IP but it will just be another random number the chances of it being your old one are impossbile.

Anyway i will tell you…

Unplug you router, computer and cable modem from the wall. Make sure nothing to do with your interent is plugged in. Leave it off over night then turn it on in the morning. You should have a new IP.

NOTE: You may have to reconfigure your router!
